he `key` if the `key` exists. Otherwise, add the `key-value` pair to the cache. If the number of keys exceeds the `capacity` from this operation, **evict** the least recently used key.\n\nThe functions `get` and `put` must each run in `O(1)` average time complexity.\n\n**Example 1:**\n\nInput\n[\"LRUCache\", \"put\", \"put\", \"get\", \"put\", \"get\", \"put\", \"get\", \"get\", \"get\"]\n[[2], [1, 1], [2, 2], [1], [3, 3], [2], [4, 4], [1], [3], [4]]\nOutput\n[null, null, null, 1, null, -1, null, -1, 3, 4]\n\nExplanation\nLRUCache lRUCache = new LRUCache(2);\nlRUCache.put(1, 1); // cache is {1=1}\nlRUCache.put(2, 2); // cache is {1=1, 2=2}\nlRUCache.get(1);    // return 1\nlRUCache.put(3, 3); // LRU key was 2, evicts key 2, cache is {1=1, 3=3}\nlRUCache.get(2);    // returns -1 (not found)\nlRUCache.put(4, 4); // LRU key was 1, evicts key 1, cache is {4=4, 3=3}\nlRUCache.get(1);    // return -1 (not found)\nlRUCache.get(3);    // return 3\nlRUCache.get(4);    // return 4\n\n**Constraints:**\n\n- `1 <= capacity <= 3000`\n\n- `0 <= key <= 10⁴`\n\n- `0 <= value <= 10⁵`\n\n- At most `2 * 10⁵` calls will be made to `get` and `put`.","problemLink":"https://leetcode.com/problems/lru-cache/","problemName":"LRU Cache","problemNumber":146,"problemSlug":"lru-cache","schemaVersion":2,"sequenceIndex":146,"solutionApproaches":[]},{"assets":[{"assetIndex":0,"bytes":91950,"contentType":"image/gif","localPath":"leetcode_seed/assets/problems/0147-insertion-sort-list/147-Insertion-sort-example-300px.gif","originalUrl":"../../../images/147-Insertion-sort-example-300px.gif","sha256":"7016a1adb268e72970adef82b8f6472ad358fd325f6baa77b3e9391abb3a40f3"},{"assetIndex":1,"bytes":15326,"contentType":"image/jpeg","localPath":"leetcode_seed/assets/problems/0147-insertion-sort-list/147-sort1linked-list.jpg","originalUrl":"../../../images/147-sort1linked-list.jpg","sha256":"bca971b2c013916213f079f286cc6417b856799516cd158bb86a48129b7591ad"},{"assetIndex":2,"bytes":19245,"contentType":"image/jpeg","